@section @code{_close_r}---Reentrant version of close
@findex _close_r
@strong{Synopsis}
@example
#include <reent.h>
int _close_r(struct _reent *@var{ptr}, int @var{fd});

@end example
@strong{Description}@*
This is a reentrant version of @code{close}.  It
takes a pointer to the global data block, which holds
@code{errno}.

